	<h2>Contact</h2>
	<div class="content" style="min-height: 250px">

	<div style="float: right; margin: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: xx-small; font-weight: bold">
	<img src="../gfx/pass.jpg" alt="Pass" title="Pass" />
	</div>

	<p>
		My preferred way of contact is per email at: <a href="mailto:Jeroen%20Massar%20%3cjeroen@massar.ch%3e">Jeroen Massar &lt;jeroen@massar.ch</a>.
	</p>
	<p>
		Like most other people I don't like spam, as such that address is
		filtered by the excellent <a href="http://spamassassin.apache.org">SpamAssassin</a>.
		The policy is set to reject all viruses and spam during SMTP-DATA thus I won't see them.
		PGP signing and encrypting your email makes sure that the message passes.
	</p>
	<p>
		I keep work, hobby and private strictly separated and thus communications which try to come through the wrong channel are silently ignored.
	</p>
	</div>

